  "description": "Welcome to your private sky sanctuary in the exclusive Soul Marbella complex. This brand-new 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom penthouse boasts panoramic sea and golf course views from every angle, blending sleek modern design with resort-style luxury. Sunlight floods the elegant open-plan interiors, where floor-to-ceiling glass invites the outdoors in and connects effortlessly to a private rooftop terrace made for elevated living.\n\nThe show-stopping rooftop space is a true highlight—featuring a private pool with built-in seating, bespoke outdoor kitchen, covered dining area, and a stylish lounge zone perfect for unforgettable sunsets. Whether entertaining or unwinding, this space offers unmatched privacy and luxury in one of Marbella’s most desirable locations.\n\nInside, both bedrooms are spacious and serene, with fitted wardrobes and refined bathrooms finished with high-end fixtures and walk-in showers. The kitchen is fully equipped with top-of-the-line appliances and opens into a bright living area framed by stunning natural views.\n\nResidents of the Soul complex enjoy world-class amenities including both indoor and outdoor pools, a spa, and gym, all surrounded by beautifully maintained gardens. With secure parking, 24-hour security, and a location just minutes from the beach, Marbellas old town, and prestigious golf courses, this penthouse is a rare find on the Costa del Sol.\n\nPlease note that we welcome families and couples only, no groups under 30, and no hen or stag parties. Should you fall outside of this category but wish to book nonetheless, please send us an enquiry detailing a bit more about yourself and the group that you will be travelling with so we can request this for you.",
